    "en": {
      "title": "Sajith announced that he will contest the presidential election",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Opposition leader Sajith Premadasa has said that he will contest in the presidential election.",
        "Sajith Premadasa said this in a post on his official Twitter page.",
        "Meanwhile, United People's Shakti had decided that opposition leader Sajith Premadasa should contest the presidential election.",
        "A meeting was held today (15) among the members of Parliament of United People's Shakti. Meanwhile, this decision was taken. (a)"
